Author: MrSpasybo
Title: [ANN][ICO] Agent Not Needed - Software live - Sell Property Without An Agent
Body: The platform uses ICR + TLSC + ICO Sale to regulate ANN tokens. Investors can only buy tokens in ICO and IRC, TLSC can only receive tokens, then when TLSC reaches 90%, you will have a new ICO to raise fund. So you control the whole platform, so do you lose the decentralized nature of the blockchain?

Author: AgentNotNeeded
Title: [ANN][ICO] Agent Not Needed - Software live - Sell Property Without An Agent
Body: The ICR (Internal Core Reserve) is setup so if a platform user needs add tokens then 50% of purchase come from us so that our company can generate revenue to pay costs, pay staff wages etc. This account can only send tokens to the TLSC so the community can rest assured that any tokens we as a company hold won't be dumped on any exchange and also that we do not control the tokens. The ICR can only send tokens to the TLSC.  The TLSC (Time Locked Smart Contract) is where any ANN tokens that are spent on the platform go. All tokens that are spent on the platform are sent to this account which will be setup to only be able to receive tokens not send them. The reason is the same as for the ICR account, it takes away any control of the tokens by our company so that the community can be assured that we cannot send those tokens anywhere or dump them on an exchange. Once the TLSC accumulates 90% of all ANN tokens in existence  then it will allow us to run another token sale at that point with the price per token being the price at that time.  The reason there are two separate accounts with limited functionality is because the ICR is the tokens we as a company are selling through our internal marketplace whilst the TLSC is where all ANN tokens end up.   We have no control over ANN tokens, the price of ANN tokens will depend on public demand just like any other cryptocurrency, the above was designed to assure our community that we have no intention to dump any tokens which the smart contract will prove. No need to take our word and trust our words, the smart contract takes away any control we might have which we have done as a sign that we don't want to control and can't control the ANN tokens we hold or accumulate.

Author: kingofcommerce
Title: [ANN][ICO] Agent Not Needed - Software live - Sell Property Without An Agent
Body: WEBSITE            BLOG            TWITTER            FACEBOOK         WHITEPAPER         ANNOUNCEMENT  REDDIT   TOKEN MAIN TOKEN SALE STARTING ON: 1st MARCH TOKEN MAIN TOKEN ENDS STARTING ON: 31st MARCH    Agent Not Needed ( ANN ) Token Sale Now Live!  We Are Building The UK's First Peer To Peer Property Portal   Our peer to peer property marketplace is now live. Buy, sell or rent a property without the need for an estate agent.  VISIT PROPERTY MARKETPLACE  VISIT TOKENSALE WEBSITE  VIEW WHITEPAPER  VIEW BOUNTY PROGRAM    Agent Not Needed is a peer to peer property platform that allows buyers and sellers to transact property directly without the need for estate agents.  Our grand vision is to build a peer to peer property platform built on blockchain where you can buy, sell and rent property directly without the need for estate agents, solicitors or conveyors and utilize AI and machine learning to improve the efficiency of sales on our platform and further improve our product and concept. We will work towards achieving this vision in phases across the next 5 years.    Roadmap     We believe our property platform will revolutionise the entire property industry and it will provide choice to individuals with how they wish to transact property. It will make the property transactions faster, cheaper and more efficient, whilst the use of blockchain technology will reduce the risk of fraud and smart contracts will reduce human error and used with escrow to decrease the failure rate of property transactions and failure rate in the chain. We will also provide real time tracking of the property transaction process.   The UK HM Land Registry have released a business strategy document to have their own blockchain built for land registry by 2022 with the mission “To become the world’s leading land registry for speed, simplicity and an open approach to data”. Once completed, we will look to implement our blockchain platform with the government blockchain to complete the land registry.  Agent Not Needed will first be available to the UK allowing individuals to buy and sell property with the plan to later expand into other English speaking countries such as the US, Canada and Australia, adding our property rental solution to the platform and then to expand to other global non English speaking countries around the world.  Version One of our property platform (released): www.agentnotneeded.com          More details to follow including Bounty Program and Bonus Structure    Official Forum Usernames  KINGOFCOMMERCE AGENTNOTNEEDED

Title: [ANN][ICO] Agent Not Needed - Software live - Sell Property Without An Agent
Body: Hello,  My only question is why do you need a token, let alone your own token for a per to per property portal? Why can't you an already existing infrastructure, such as Hyperledger?

Author: NoAgentNeeded
Title: [ANN][ICO] Agent Not Needed - Software live - Sell Property Without An Agent
Body: Hi, thanks for your question.  Ok basically right now in the UK the government doesn't allow for property sales to be completed on the blockchain though they are in discussion to change that legislation and are looking to work with private companies in that area to help create that solution (Source).  The token sale is to help us raise the funds to complete our property portal as we planned to use tokens on the platform anyway as platform credits. We are 90% complete with our beta version but for the full version we need further funding. Once the UK Government have changed legislation to allow property transactions to be completed using the blockchain, we will make a decision on whether to build on the blockchain or use hyperledger based on the need of the industry. We are creating an ERC20 token which can be used on the platform to sell or rent property on the platform, advertise on the platform or sell to other users on the platform.  Petros
